    <item>
      <title>印度出口民意调查预测莫迪将在邦选举中遭遇激烈斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/india-exit-polls-predict-tough-fight-for-modi-in-state-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党将面临一场充满挑战的竞争，出口民意调查显示，他在五个州选举中的两次选举中仅取得微弱优势，这表明他明年重返权力宝座将面临一场艰苦的斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/india-exit-polls-predict-tough-fight-for-modi-in-state-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:15:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上诉法院恢复特朗普在纽约欺诈案中的禁言令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/trump-gag-order-in-ny-fraud-case-reinstated-by-appeals-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约一家上诉法院恢复了一系列禁言令，禁止唐纳德·特朗普及其律师公开评论监督该州针对前总统的民事欺诈审判的法官的法律助理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/trump-gag-order-in-ny-fraud-case-reinstated-by-appeals-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:05:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞安航空首席执行官奥利里谴责爱尔兰对都柏林骚乱的反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/ryanair-chief-o-leary-blasts-irish-response-to-dublin-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞安航空控股公司首席执行官迈克尔·奥利里表示，爱尔兰政府等待太久才解决导致上周都柏林骚乱的因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/ryanair-chief-o-leary-blasts-irish-response-to-dublin-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:56:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯访问以色列，敦促领导人遵守国际法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/blinken-visits-israel-presses-leaders-to-obey-international-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周四与以色列领导人会面，强调一旦加沙战事恢复，就必须遵守国际法，这一语气转变凸显了美国对摧毁哈马斯行动所造成的人道主义伤亡日益担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/blinken-visits-israel-presses-leaders-to-obey-international-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:53:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的乔治·桑托斯在众议院驱逐投票前猛烈抨击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/embattled-george-santos-lashes-out-ahead-of-expulsion-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[被起诉的纽约众议员乔治·桑托斯周四对其他大多数未透露姓名的议员的不当行为进行了一系列影射，并暗示他可能有一天会重返公职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/embattled-george-santos-lashes-out-ahead-of-expulsion-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 14:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登未兑现的访问非洲的誓言再次引发了被忽视的感觉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/biden-s-unfilled-vow-to-visit-africa-renews-feelings-of-neglect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统将通过接待安哥拉总统若昂·洛伦索来寻求展示美国对非洲的兴趣，但他们周四的会面却让人们关注拜登尚未兑现的访问非洲大陆的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/biden-s-unfilled-vow-to-visit-africa-renews-feelings-of-neglect</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 14:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟拟在疑虑中公布动用被冻结俄罗斯资产的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/eu-aims-to-unveil-plan-to-tap-frozen-russian-assets-amid-doubts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管一些成员国对此表示担忧，欧盟仍在推进一项提议，对俄罗斯央行冻结的超过 2000 亿欧元（合 2180 亿美元）资产的利润征税，以援助乌克兰的重建。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/eu-aims-to-unveil-plan-to-tap-frozen-russian-assets-amid-doubts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 13:37:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦计划征收财富税和新的锂税以增加收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/zimbabwe-plans-14-fold-increase-in-spending-to-aid-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦征收新的锂税和财富税，为支出增加近 14 倍提供资金，旨在提振预计明年将放缓的经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/zimbabwe-plans-14-fold-increase-in-spending-to-aid-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 13:35:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长的困境如此严重，连安德鲁·科莫都在考虑竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/nyc-mayor-s-woes-are-so-bad-even-andrew-cuomo-is-eyeing-a-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 遭受一系列打击后，政治血腥味十足，潜在的挑战者正在权衡是否要发起进攻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/nyc-mayor-s-woes-are-so-bad-even-andrew-cuomo-is-eyeing-a-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
